"'''Emanations of Darkness'''" was a short story written by [[Patricia A. Jackson]] concerning the final fate of her characters [[Adalric Cessius Brandl]], [[Jaalib Brandl]], and [[Fable Astin/Legends|Fable Astin]]. She submitted it originally for the ''[[Star Wars Adventure Journal]]'', but [[West End Games]] stopped producing the journal before the story could be printed. It was later submitted to the ''[[Star Wars Gamer]]'' magazine, where it was turned down for unknown reasons. Because of this, Patricia Jackson posted the story online, where it is available for all to read.

